  "remarks": "TAi.093 Title: a) Maulavi  b) Mullah. Designation: a) Governor of Herat Province under the Taliban regime  b) Spokesperson of the Taliban regime  c) Governor of Kabul province under the Taliban regime  d) Minister of Internal Affairs under the Taliban regime. Belongs to Popalzai tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 23 Jul. 2010; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 January 2001 (amended on 21 Sep 2007 and 3 Oct. 2008, 12 Apr. 2010, 29 Nov. 2011 and 31. Dec 2013, 7 Sep. 2016)",
